title: JUST DANCE AT THE AUSTRALIAN OPEN OF SURFING
description:
Hurley -- Australian Open of Surfing -- Manly 2012 -- Day 7
You've heard of dancing in the streets but dancing on the beach? Blue Juice, Sneaky Sound System, Children Collide and The Living End make the beach erupt.
